=load driver on detecting device=
1) Build the module, create a symbolic link in /lib/modules/'uname-r'/xx folder
2) Do depmod -a
3) Make sure that the 'alias' string found when 'modinfo module_name' is issued, is added in /lib/modules/'uname-r'/modules.alias

=udev rules=
To add a new udev rule, add a file in /etc/udev/rules.d folder
